              sphere. Our expressions are valid for all exposure times,
              irrespective of the size of the confining space and the value of
              the diffusion coefficient. They apply also in the common case
              where the exposure time is smaller than the time-lapse due, e.g.,
              to ``dead time'' caused by the readout process in the camera.
